channel.title: How to change the teleport places!
channel.description:
if anybody wants to know to change the teleporting places on devolution source go on client.java, hold ctr and f and search the coords of the teleporting spot.
[code=cpp]triggerTele(X, Y, 0, false);[/code]
something along those lines should come up.
change the X coords and Y coords to what you want then save compile and run
